title: Reappointment Of Commissioner For Uniform Legal Services Regulation (Premier of Victoria)
text: ( Source : Premier of Victoria ) Attorney-General Martin Pakula today announced the reappointment of Dale Boucher as the Commissioner for Uniform Legal Services Regulation. Mr Boucher was appointed as the inaugural Commissioner on 29 September
